R - restart the game
W -to select white coins
B -to select Black Coins
Left arrow - to move sticker left
Right arrow - to move sticker Right
Up arrow - to increase speed of sticker
down arrow -to decrease spped of sticker
a - to change angle of sticker in anticlock wise direction
c- to change angle of sticker in clock wise direction
space - to move the sticker

How to Play:
Select Whites or Blacks first
use left or right arrow to change position of sticker
use a or c to change direction of sticker
use up or down arrow to change speed of sticker
after choosing all atributes of sticker use space for its motion
